621
00:44:26,600 --> 00:44:27,633
[Desk]

622
00:44:27,633 --> 00:44:29,800
I stepped over it.

623
00:44:29,800 --> 00:44:34,300
Then I saw the child sleeping

624
00:44:34,933 --> 00:44:37,000
